location.fullValue: Granite Plan, Fieldstone at Gladden Farms - Premier Series

data.description: Just move in and unpack in this amazing Energy-efficient home built in 2022!  The kitchen features 36in DUSK cabinets, complimented by ASHEN WHITE granite as well as ALLURE pendant lights to accent the expansive kitchen island. The ceramic tile is a 15x15 BELCLAIRE WHITE extended flooring with carpet in bedrooms only and matching DUSK cabinets finish the laundry room. Wonderful primary suite, tucked away at the back of the home with its own hallway. A great backyard with a covered patio, artificial grass and pavers finishes off this fantastic home. Community amenities include a splash pad, community garden, dog park and greenbelts. All of this is located in the highly sought-after Marana Unified School District.
